{"tid":478764,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［兩陣對壘］學生動源10人與珍惜群組20人隔馬示威","createTime":"2017-11-24T11:35:52.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-24T11:52:56.000Z","uid":41351,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"d25ab437d69f722a6ec4c4b0aec0e5577221bfce","tid":478764,"uid":41351,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-24T11:35:52.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://on.cc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fon.cc&d=P7RVNT%2BZnjVYvEPP2GZcpzPUa9iY%2BpOmOVTB4fMSqaQ%3D&h=1c6ec260\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">on.cc</a>東網專訊】有組織今天(24日)到葵青區一所中學派發傳單，並聲援早前於活動上展示「香港獨立」相片的中學生，惟校外有持相反意見的團體在場，雙方一度爆發罵戰。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n早前有中學生出席活動與政府官員合照時展示港獨標語，其後遭校方警告。組織「學生動源」及「香港民族陣線」約10人到該校請願，部分請願人士身穿校服，並要求校方道歉，認為校方做法無理，因為學生擁有言論及表達自由。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n然而，持相反意見的珍惜群組，逾20人一早到達現場支持校方，並反對有人煽動港獨，最終雙方爆發罵戰。校方最終改為安排後門予該校學生放學，而現場亦有警方分隔兩邊示威者。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n請願團體於傍晚6時15分離開。學生動源召集人鍾先生認為行動失敗，因為校方未有正視其訴求作出道歉，而且未能見到涉事學生；惟他表示，不排除日後再到該校表達訴求，亦明言未來會到不同學校宣傳港獨信息。<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/24/193527_e638fbabd8ce2cdf9148a31834db63bf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F24%2F193527_e638fbabd8ce2cdf9148a31834db63bf.jpg&h=7b70941b&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/24/193530_6ecde1dc81c75b27fbd236c5ef28157e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F24%2F193530_6ecde1dc81c75b27fbd236c5ef28157e.jpg&h=071c6350&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/24/193533_fde49f74fb6bcf54d5ba91cd7d952083.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F24%2F193533_fde49f74fb6bcf54d5ba91cd7d952083.jpg&h=11cbe2a2&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/24/193535_499eaa278a9b4105663b744c9b13ab8e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F24%2F193535_499eaa278a9b4105663b744c9b13ab8e.jpg&h=451ca49a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n---"},{"pid":"1863043be6131450657bb6e226038c38de900ea1","tid":478764,"uid":41351,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-24T11:38:04.000Z","msg":"廢老又阻頭阻勢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4522c36573174c6f1ce2cb39026f3eb19e06163c","tid":478764,"uid":9284,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-24T11:41:58.000Z","msg":"10人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c916c476245da919ea8d1b0f7f6b5bda75d8767","tid":478764,"uid":53498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-24T11:52:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>廢老又阻頭阻勢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n班仆街拎綜援做兼職啦"}]}